r pdf document."&gt;	<br>			&lt;/cfif&gt;</p><p>		&lt;/cfif&gt;<br>	&lt;/cfif&gt;</p><p>Let me know if you need the entire sample file.</p><p>Cheers,<br>Ilir</p></div>
